overview.en: RDAO is the governance token for the RChain DAO community, a group of RChain technology enthusiasts and ecosystem builders. *Disclaimer: RDAO and RChain Cooperative do not have any legal or business relationships.
overview.zh: RDAO 是 RChain DAO 社区的治理代币，是由 RChain 技术爱好者和生态系统建设者组成的团体。*免责声明：RDAO 和 RChain 合作社没有任何法律或商业关系。
